data.name: DictionaryListEventFlags
desc: constants representing a single dictionary-list event.
These flags define the possible types for a dictionary-list event.

items.name: ADD_POS_ENTRY
lines: A positive entry was added to a dictionary from the dictionary list.

items.name: DEL_POS_ENTRY
lines: A positive entry was deleted from a dictionary of the dictionary-list or a dictionary with positive entries was cleared.

items.name: ADD_NEG_ENTRY
lines: A negative entry was added to a dictionary from the dictionary-list.

items.name: DEL_NEG_ENTRY
lines: A negative entry was deleted from a dictionary of the dictionary-list or a dictionary with negative entries was cleared.

items.name: ACTIVATE_POS_DIC
lines: A dictionary with positive entries was activated or has changed its language.

items.name: DEACTIVATE_POS_DIC
lines: A dictionary with positive entries was deactivated or has changed its language.

items.name: ACTIVATE_NEG_DIC
lines: A dictionary with negative entries was activated or has changed its language.

items.name: DEACTIVATE_NEG_DIC
lines: A dictionary with negative entries was deactivated or has changed its language.
